## 4. Dagster Assets

### Asset Naming
| Type | Pattern | Example |
|------|---------|---------|
| Raw | `raw_{source}_{entity}` | `raw_jira_issues` |
| Clean | `clean_{source}_{entity}` | `clean_jira_issues` |
| Metrics | `metrics_{metric_name}` | `metrics_lead_time` |

### Asset Structure

```python
from dagster import asset, AssetExecutionContext

@asset(
    group_name="jira",           # Group in UI
    compute_kind="dlt",          # Badge in UI
    description="Load issues from Jira API"
)
def raw_jira_issues(context: AssetExecutionContext) -> None:
    """Load Jira issues to raw layer."""
