## 5. Naming Conventions

| Entity | Format | Example |
|--------|--------|---------|
| Files, functions, variables | `snake_case` | `jira_client.py`, `get_issues()` |
| Classes | `PascalCase` | `JiraConfig`, `Integration` |
| Constants | `UPPER_CASE` | `MAX_RETRIES`, `API_TIMEOUT` |
| DB schemas | `snake_case` | `raw_jira`, `clean_jira`, `metrics` |
| DB tables | `snake_case` | `issues`, `sprints`, `users` |
| Materialized views | `mv_{name}` | `mv_lead_time`, `mv_velocity` |
| Dagster assets | `{layer}_{source}_{entity}` | `raw_jira_issues` |
| API endpoints | `/api/v1/{resource}` | `/api/v1/integrations` |

