## 8. API Design

### REST Conventions
```
GET    /api/v1/integrations          # List all
POST   /api/v1/integrations          # Create
GET    /api/v1/integrations/{id}     # Get one
PUT    /api/v1/integrations/{id}     # Update
DELETE /api/v1/integrations/{id}     # Delete

POST   /api/v1/integrations/{id}/sync   # Trigger action
```

### Response Format
```python
# Success
{"data": {...}, "meta": {"total": 10, "page": 1}}

# Error
{"detail": "Integration not found", "code": "NOT_FOUND"}
```

